---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="咨询服务 — MR.QuanweiDU" description="帮助你在混沌中找到方向。一对一深度咨询，从问题到行动。">

<div class="hero">
  <p class="hero-label">Consulting Service · 咨询服务</p>
  <h1>Clarity is<br>a <em>strategy.</em></h1>
  <p class="hero-sub">帮助你在混沌中找到方向。一对一深度咨询，从问题到行动。</p>
  <div class="hero-actions">
    <a href="#contact" class="btn-primary">立即预约</a>
    <a href="#services" class="btn-ghost">了解服务</a>
  </div>
  <div class="hero-scroll">
    <div class="scroll-line"></div>
    <span class="scroll-text">Scroll</span>
  </div>
</div>

<section id="about">
  <div class="section-label">关于我</div>
  <div class="about-grid">
    <div>
      <h2>Thinking is<br>a <em>craft.</em></h2>
      <div class="about-stats reveal">
        <div>
          <div class="stat-num">200+</div>
          <div class="stat-label">完成咨询</div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="stat-num">98%</div>
          <div class="stat-label">客户满意度</div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="stat-num">5+</div>
          <div class="stat-label">年经验</div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="stat-num">3</div>
          <div class="stat-label">服务类型</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="about-text reveal">
      <p>我相信大多数问题，本质上是思维问题。混乱来自于框架的缺失，而不是信息的不足。</p>
      <p>通过系统性的对话，我帮助你把模糊的困境转化为清晰的问题，再从清晰的问题找到可执行的路径。</p>
      <p>不给你答案。帮你找到属于你自己的答案。</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="services-wrap" id="services">
  <div class="services-inner">
    <div class="section-label reveal">服务内容</div>
    <div class="services-grid">
      <div class="service-card reveal">
        <div class="service-num">No. 01</div>
        <div class="service-title">Single Session</div>
        <div class="service-title-zh">单次深度咨询</div>
        <div class="service-desc">60分钟，聚焦一个核心问题。适合有明确困惑、需要外部视角的你。</div>
        <div class="service-price">¥ 599 / 次</div>
      </div>
      <div class="service-card reveal">
        <div class="service-num">No. 02</div>
        <div class="service-title">Monthly Retainer</div>
        <div class="service-title-zh">月度持续陪跑</div>
        <div class="service-desc">每月4次咨询 + 随时文字支持。适合处于重要转折期、需要持续思考伙伴的你。</div>
        <div class="service-price">¥ 1,999 / 月</div>
      </div>
      <div class="service-card reveal">
        <div class="service-num">No. 03</div>
        <div class="service-title">Deep Dive</div>
        <div class="service-title-zh">季度深度项目</div>
        <div class="service-desc">3个月结构化咨询，从系统层面重建思维框架。适合想彻底改变某个领域的你。</div>
        <div class="service-price">¥ 4,999 / 季</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<section id="process">
  <div class="section-label reveal">工作流程</div>
  <div class="process-list">
    <div class="process-item reveal">
      <div class="process-title">申请</div>
      <div class="process-desc">填写预约表单，简述你的情况和期待。我会在48小时内回复。</div>
    </div>
    <div class="process-item reveal">
      <div class="process-title">匹配</div>
      <div class="process-desc">15分钟免费通话，确认我们是否适合合作，选择合适的服务类型。</div>
    </div>
    <div class="process-item reveal">
      <div class="process-title">咨询</div>
      <div class="process-desc">线上视频进行，结束后我会发送谈话摘要和行动建议。</div>
    </div>
    <div class="process-item reveal">
      <div class="process-title">跟进</div>
      <div class="process-desc">每次咨询后持续跟进，确保行动落地，不止于谈话本身。</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="testimonials-wrap">
  <div class="testimonials-inner">
    <div class="section-label reveal">他们说</div>
    <div class="testimonials-grid">
      <div class="testimonial reveal">
        <div class="testimonial-quote">"</div>
        <div class="testimonial-text">一次对话让我想清楚了纠结了半年的问题。不是给了我答案，而是帮我看清楚了自己真正想要什么。</div>
        <div class="testimonial-author">— L.W. · 创业者</div>
      </div>
      <div class="testimonial reveal">
        <div class="testimonial-quote">"</div>
        <div class="testimonial-text">我以为我的问题很复杂，结果发现只是缺少一个清晰的框架。三个月后，一切都不同了。</div>
        <div class="testimonial-author">— M.C. · 产品经理</div>
      </div>
      <div class="testimonial reveal">
        <div class="testimonial-quote">"</div>
        <div class="testimonial-text">他不会告诉你该怎么做，但结束之后你会清楚地知道自己该怎么做。这种感觉很奇妙。</div>
        <div class="testimonial-author">— R.Z. · 自由撰稿人</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<section id="faq">
  <div class="section-label reveal">常见问题</div>
  <div class="faq-list">
    <div class="faq-item reveal">
      <div class="faq-q">
        <span class="faq-q-text">咨询是线上还是线下？</span>
        <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-a">目前全部通过线上视频进行（微信/腾讯会议/Zoom），时区灵活安排，国内外均可。</div>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-item reveal">
      <div class="faq-q">
        <span class="faq-q-text">适合什么样的人来咨询？</span>
        <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-a">适合感到困惑、处于转折点、或者想清楚想明白某件重要事情的人。不需要你有多大的问题，只需要你有认真思考的意愿。</div>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-item reveal">
      <div class="faq-q">
        <span class="faq-q-text">如何付款？</span>
        <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-a">确认合作后通过微信/支付宝付款，付款后安排时间。单次咨询全额预付，月度/季度服务按周期付款。</div>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-item reveal">
      <div class="faq-q">
        <span class="faq-q-text">如果觉得不适合可以退款吗？</span>
        <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-a">15分钟免费通话就是为了确认匹配度。如果咨询开始后你觉得没有帮助，可以在第一次结束后申请退款，无条件。</div>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-item reveal">
      <div class="faq-q">
        <span class="faq-q-text">目前还有名额吗？</span>
        <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-a">每月只接受有限数量的新客户，以保证质量。请通过预约表单申请，我会告知当前是否有空位。</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="cta-wrap" id="contact">
  <h2>Ready to think<br><em>clearly?</em></h2>
  <a href="mailto:3690413@gmail.com" class="btn-primary">发送邮件预约 →</a>
</div>

</Layout>

<script>
  // FAQ toggle
  document.querySelectorAll('.faq-q').forEach(q => {
    q.addEventListener('click', () => {
      const item = q.closest('.faq-item');
      const isOpen = item.classList.contains('open');
      document.querySelectorAll('.faq-item').forEach(i => i.classList.remove('open'));
      if (!isOpen) item.classList.add('open');
    });
  });

  // Scroll reveal
  const observer = new IntersectionObserver((entries) => {
    entries.forEach((entry, i) => {
      if (entry.isIntersecting) {
        setTimeout(() => entry.target.classList.add('visible'), i * 80);
        observer.unobserve(entry.target);
      }
    });
  }, { threshold: 0.1 });

  document.querySelectorAll('.reveal').forEach(el => observer.observe(el));
</script>

<style>
  /* HERO */
  .hero {
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 120px 60px 80px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .hero::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: -200px; right: -200px;
    width: 600px; height: 600px;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(138,106,58,0.04) 0%, transparent 70%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .hero-label {
    font-family: var(--serif-en);
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.3em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--ink-ghost);
    margin-bottom: 48px;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeUp 0.6s ease 0.1s forwards;
  }

  .hero h1 {
    font-family: var(--serif-en);
    font-size: clamp(48px, 7vw, 96px);
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.1;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    color: var(--ink);
    max-width: 800px;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeUp 0.6s ease 0.2s forwards;
  }

  .hero h1 em { font-style: italic; color: var(--ink-light); }

  .hero-sub {
    margin-top: 40px;
    font-size: 16px;
    color: var(--ink-light);
    max-width: 480px;
    line-height: 2;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeUp 0.6s ease 0.3s forwards;
  }

  .hero-actions {
    margin-top: 56px;
    display: flex;
    gap: 20px;
    align-items: center;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeUp 0.6s ease 0.4s forwards;
  }

  .btn-primary {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 14px 36px;
    background: var(--ink);
    color: var(--bg);
    font-family: var(--serif-en);
    font-size: 13px;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .btn-primary:hover { opacity: 0.8; }

  .btn-ghost {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 14px 36px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule);
    color: var(--ink-ghost);
    font-family: var(--serif-en);
    font-size: 13px;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .btn-ghost:hover { color: var(--ink); border-color: var(--ink); }

  .hero-scroll {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 48px;
    left: 60px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 16px;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeUp 0.8s ease 1.2s forwards;
  }

  .scroll-line { width: 40px; height: 1px; background: var(--rule); }

  .scroll-text {
    font-family: var(--serif-en);
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.25em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--ink-ghost);
  }

  /* SECTIONS */
  section {
    padding: 120px 60px;
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .section-label {
    font-family: var(--serif-en);
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.35em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--ink-ghost);
    margin-bottom: 64px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 20px;
  }

  .section-label::after {
    content: '';
    flex: 1;
    max-width: 60px;
    height: 1px;
    background: var(--rule);
  }

  /* ABOUT */
  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 80px;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .about-grid h2 {
    font-family: var(--serif-en);
    font-size: clamp(32px, 4vw, 52px);
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.2;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    color: var(--ink);
  }

  .about-grid h2 em { font-style: italic; color: var(--ink-light); }

  .about-text { font-size: 15px; color: var(--ink-light); line-height: 2.2; }
  .about-text p + p { margin-top: 24px; }

  .about-stats {
    margin-top: 48px;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 32px;
  }

  .stat-num {
    font-family: var(--serif-en);
    font-size: 40px;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--ink);
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .stat-label { font-size: 12px; color: var(--ink-ghost); margin-top: 8px; letter-spacing: 0.05em; }

  /* SERVICES */
  .services-wrap { background: var(--bg-alt, #faf9f7); padding: 120px 0; }
  .services-inner { max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 60px; }

  .services-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 2px;
  }

  .service-card {
    padding: 48px 40px;
    border: 1px solid var(--rule);
    transition: border-color 0.3s ease;
  }

  .service-card:hover { border-color: var(--ink-ghost); }

  .service-num {
    font-family: var(--serif-en);
    font-size: 11px;
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--ink-ghost);
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }

  .service-title { font-family: var(--serif-en); font-size: 22px; font-weight: 400; color: var(--ink); margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .service-title-zh { font-size: 13px; color: var(--ink-ghost); margin-bottom: 24px; }
  .service-desc { font-size: 14px; color: var(--ink-light); line-height: 2; }

  .service-price {
    margin-top: 32px;
    padding-top: 24px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--rule);
    font-family: var(--serif-en);
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--ink);
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  /* PROCESS */
  .process-list {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 40px;
    counter-reset: step;
  }

  .process-item {
    counter-increment: step;
    padding-top: 32px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--rule);
  }

  .process-item::before {
    content: '0' counter(step);
    font-family: var(--serif-en);
    font-size: 11px;
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--ink-ghost);
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .process-title { font-family: var(--serif-en); font-size: 18px; font-weight: 400; color: var(--ink); margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .process-desc { font-size: 13px; color: var(--ink-light); line-height: 2; }

  /* TESTIMONIALS */
  .testimonials-wrap { background: var(--bg-alt, #faf9f7); padding: 120px 0; }
  .testimonials-inner { max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 60px; }
  .testimonials-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 32px; }

  .testimonial { padding: 40px; border: 1px solid var(--rule); }

  .testimonial-quote {
    font-family: var(--serif-en);
    font-size: 32px;
    color: var(--ink-ghost);
    opacity: 0.4;
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .testimonial-text { font-size: 14px; color: var(--ink-light); line-height: 2.2; font-style: italic; }

  .testimonial-author {
    margin-top: 28px;
    padding-top: 20px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--rule);
    font-family: var(--serif-en);
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--ink-ghost);
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  /* FAQ */
  .faq-list { max-width: 720px; }
  .faq-item { border-top: 1px solid var(--rule); padding: 28px 0; }
  .faq-item:last-child { border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule); }

  .faq-q { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; cursor: pointer; gap: 24px; }

  .faq-q-text { font-family: var(--serif-en); font-size: 17px; font-weight: 400; color: var(--ink); }

  .faq-icon {
    width: 20px; height: 20px;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    font-family: var(--serif-en);
    font-size: 16px;
    color: var(--ink-ghost);
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
  }

  .faq-item.open .faq-icon { transform: rotate(45deg); }

  .faq-a {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--ink-light);
    line-height: 2.2;
    max-height: 0;
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: max-height 0.4s ease, padding 0.3s ease;
  }

  .faq-item.open .faq-a { max-height: 300px; padding-top: 20px; }

  /* CTA */
  .cta-wrap { text-align: center; padding: 160px 60px; }

  .cta-wrap h2 {
    font-family: var(--serif-en);
    font-size: clamp(40px, 6vw, 80px);
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.15;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto 48px;
    color: var(--ink);
  }

  .cta-wrap h2 em { font-style: italic; color: var(--ink-light); }

  /* ANIMATIONS */
  @keyframes fadeUp {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(24px); }
    to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }

  .reveal {
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(32px);
    transition: opacity 0.8s ease, transform 0.8s ease;
  }

  .reveal.visible { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }

  /* MOBILE */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .hero { padding: 100px 24px 60px; }
    .hero-scroll { left: 24px; }
    section { padding: 80px 24px; }
    .about-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 48px; }
    .services-inner, .testimonials-inner { padding: 0 24px; }
    .services-wrap, .testimonials-wrap { padding: 80px 0; }
    .services-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .testimonials-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .process-list { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
    .cta-wrap { padding: 100px 24px; }
  }
</style>
